<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OpenSwift Secure Access Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: left;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #4285F4;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .otp {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #1a73e8;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 2px solid #1a73e8;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .important {
            color: #d93025;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555555;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="title">AnoTS Secure Access Code</div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{username}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>We trust this message finds you in good health. In response to your recent request, we are pleased to share the <span class="important">Secure Access Code</span> for your AnoTS account:</p>
            <div class="otp">{{OTP}}</div>
            <p class="message">Kindly handle this confidential code with the utmost care and refrain from sharing it with unauthorized individuals. The code is valid for <strong>15 minutes</strong> and is exclusively for secure access to your AnoTS account.</p>
            <p>If you did not initiate this request, please contact our dedicated support team immediately for prompt assistance.</p>
        </div>
        <hr style="margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
        <p class="signature">Best regards,<br>The OpenSwift Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
